# Plan: Add PixelArt AI Provider Package

## Context

The Vercel AI SDK uses a monorepo of provider packages under `packages/<provider>/`. Each provider implements standard SDK interfaces (`ProviderV3`, `ImageModelV3`) from `@ai-sdk/provider`. The `@ai-sdk/black-forest-labs` package is the closest reference: it is an **image-only** provider that throws `NoSuchModelError` for `languageModel` and `embeddingModel`. The new `@ai-sdk/pixelart` package follows this same pattern, adding a fictional provider that hits `https://api.pixelart.ai/v1`.

---

## Files to Create

All files go under `packages/pixelart/`. **No existing files are modified.**

### 1. `packages/pixelart/package.json`

Mirror `black-forest-labs/package.json` exactly, replacing names/metadata:

```json
